Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你惹龙生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家还想好好的玩一场游戏 让矢野打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玩游戏不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为游戏都是龙的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想着要去龙家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 不知道自己做了什么惹他生气的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是上次他来的时候 我很坚决的把他赶走了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个差点被看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(621,413)}(送给龙)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点事情算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心眼太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:21:04.62,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,人员表 翻译 阿虚 老虎 时间 校译 阿虚 义工 被风早同学萌倒的诺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都怪到别人头上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天和后天 绝对不要来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 明天明明是龙的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(412,375)}(垃圾桶)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是下不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 到龙家去玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又没说今天不准去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便和他和好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日礼物也一起带去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是因为这个惹他生气 那不就没有意义了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 我爱死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常让人意外的不防守战术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的绝地反击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很强大吧 今天很强大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 所以一直没说出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是找不到时机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只要像往常一样在正月见到哥哥就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没必要特意安排千鹤和哥哥见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:05:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们才是 来这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在举行城的安慰大会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的失恋同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是正好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城和矢野的共同安慰大会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有这种事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失恋的二人在相互安慰的过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生了爱情的萌芽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是矢野吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要尊敬城了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们几个挤一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有谁能说点有趣的话题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:05:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 矢野为什么分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我点什么喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在朋友的家里过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这么多人的中间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听听别人的恋爱故事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 说起来 上次的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然见到自己喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切 全部...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在都已经不再是和我无关的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙 给我个杯子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的拉面可强大了 *&*%$#@...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便把这个给他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能高兴就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 喜欢什么类型的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸怀宽广 处变不惊的成熟男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说没在生气...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被人像那样赶出家门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会有点受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是因为龙做错了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我想把开心的事情留到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想告诉我什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么有力气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 你长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 我没听说你要回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没觉得抱歉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说明天回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为今天工作提前结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非那个就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 翔太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发这么长了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:09:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 风早 现在是我在和彻说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手嘛 龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是千鹤的朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中里的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是爽子和矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不讨厌这种类型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把矢野藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞进壁橱里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然 只穿着睡衣和牛仔裤就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(590,155)\frz356.395}(穿着这个直接就睡觉)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\frz350.77\pos(544,259)}(只是换了下裤子)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是新的也应该穿条超短裙来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说龙 为什么没告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,0:09:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗 我可以进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李只有这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的全部拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...是女朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子就是我弟弟 龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是彻的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做片山遥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 这孩子也介绍下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田千鹤 叫她小千就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候开始就像妹妹一样疼爱她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是片山 请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他们的邻居 叫做吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是家人也不是亲戚 总觉得...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 别说得那么见外嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚算啥...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得彻哥哥回来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们就一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似来的时机很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的无关人士们 赶快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个主角就这么退场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你也是无关人士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才和大家一起回家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了 再见*6
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没变嘛 我家很近嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也很强嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你想些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太 你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我在那个场合下说点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得千鹤会因为我担心她而感到沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气的话还好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一定很沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 龙一直都在担心吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是龙的错 别太失落了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是没在失落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白 我是不是真的担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很喜欢呢 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 又是我一个人赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后连续打了4小时的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指彻的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我还没有恭喜他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去见下彻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得自己一直憧憬的哥哥就要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 会有更好的男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 总觉得不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞得你们两个要提前回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得是矢野的安慰会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.94,0:15:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 那个已经完全忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已经这个时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我单相思的时间可是很长的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他现在还不会注视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要成为一个好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等长大之后 就不一定了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的是龙的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 已经起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吵醒你了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿迷你裙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 或许不是已经起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是睡不着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧 这件运动衫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥穿剩下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这里有个洞 但完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 到学校再见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为她会像以前一样哇哇大哭 然后对我们发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始还搞不清楚她是不是觉得难过...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么我们能做的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 现在的状况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能问她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是结果还是没有我们能做的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要穿迷你裙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是那么的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是安慰还是鼓励
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都没有做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没对小千说...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是在这种时候 说不出一句有用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔笑的真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说像女儿一样又不是女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说像妹妹一样又不是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的既不是亲戚也不是什么别的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这重要的合家欢乐的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻居家的孩子掺和进去算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻居家的孩子么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙 来比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(373,389)}龙 千鹤 小学三年级
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动真格的话就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙 不能弄哭女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(628,396)}彻 高二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛的痛痛的飞走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻 我抓到虫子了 快来看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻 虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻 虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.44,0:20:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的爱情表现 真不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是会对我微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻他身边的经常有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是每个交往的时间都不长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想 就算交往也不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的梦想就是成为他的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现我的梦想的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:25.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:25.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飞满了纸飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:36.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いかない　それが答えてなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:36.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走 那就是回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:39.65,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャボン玉　飛ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:39.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥皂泡泡 飘飘浮浮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:47.93,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空まではきっと届かない　うちに壊れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:47.93,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未到达天空就破灭消散而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:53.46,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いま誰知りたいの永遠じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:53.46,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我们想要的永远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:22:01.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このままずっと　いていたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:22:01.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管想要永远留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:12.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:12.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飞满了纸飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:21.93,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとつだけ見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:21.93,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只找寻到了属于我的唯一
